  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>From the picturesque towns along the Amalfi Coast and the lively Sorrento to the ancient streets of Pompeii, this escorted tour showcases the Neapolitan Riviera’s most popular sights. Explore the ancient towns, summit Vesuvius and take in the regions stunning coastlines on this tour.</span></p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>26</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/neapolitan-splendours-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
